 Hardware Connections:

Connect the ESP8266:

Connect VCC and GND of ESP8266 to a 5V power source (USB power bank).
Connect the CH_PD pin of ESP8266 to VCC.
Connect the GPIO pins of ESP8266 to the respective sensor modules (BP, Glucometer, Pulse Sensor).
Connect the Sensors:

Connect the Blood Pressure Sensor, Glucometer Sensor, and Pulse Sensor to the appropriate GPIO pins on the ESP8266.


Telegram Bot Setup:

Create a Telegram Bot:
Open the Telegram app and search for the "BotFather" user.
Start a chat with the BotFather and use the "/newbot" command to create a new bot.
Follow the instructions to set a name and username for your bot.
The BotFather will provide you with an API token; save this token for later use.
